values:
Happiness is Moms cookin'.&nbsp; Dont get me wrong, I&nbsp;LOVE&nbsp;to cook, but Mondays are just rough for me, so this was perfect.&nbsp; 

Remember the pork roast from Saturday, well the sale was only on WHOLE&nbsp;porkloins, so I&nbsp;gave the other half to mom.&nbsp; She in turn very kindly turned it into pork-shish-kebab; one of my favorite meals.&nbsp; So on Monday, after a stressful day at work, and a frutless search for a last minute gift, instead of having to go home and cook, I got to sit down and enjoy a hot dinner all ready made.&nbsp; Add some tomato curry sauce, some sauteed mushrooms,&nbsp;and a bit of whole grain bread - HEAVEN

Thanks Mom!
